    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This BMW E46 M3 is powered by the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and double VANOS variable valve timing. Power is delivered through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox to a torque-sensing limited-slip differential. The chassis remains exceptionally balanced, benefiting from an inspected rear subframe and a suspension geometry utilizing aluminum control arms and refreshed bushings for optimal kinematic response. Mechanically sound with a linear power band and a 8,000 RPM redline, this example offers the visceral feedback and analog engagement expected of a true M-division icon.",
